text: Every Singaporean son will come here one day. For you young lads who are entering, don't worry about it, enter with a positive state of mind, and your service will pass before you know it. Have fun!
Very accommodating hosts, food was decent. However no aircon. They have cute monkey there that will steal your food. Very fun experience and enjoyed my stay.
Interested to go on vacation but your broke? Welcome to tekong .free food ,free bunk and many more exciting activities
Security were tight, however facilities were 3rd class. Believe they were never really been upgraded since built many years back. Oh another thing, if you ever need to come here, good luck. Lol
